        <div class="featured-content__content-wrapper">
          <div class="featured-content__content">
            <h2 class="featured-content__title">Open Educational <br>Resources: Equity & Opportunities</h2>
                          <div class="featured-content__summary"><p>Providing all students an equitable education has been a cornerstone of NAACP since the organization&#8217;s inception. For too many years, too many children, particularly African American, other minorities, and underprivileged people from all groups have been subjected to lesser educational opportunities, leading to lesser opportunities for success in their personal and professional lives. A major contributing factor to the disparities continues to be the lack of appropriate instructional materials.</p>
</div>
